description_0: A close up view of a white and black cat's head with green eyes looking into the camera. A wooden board, which is slightly cut at the edges, is underneath the cat's chin and a black screen window is behind the cat. A silver frame is around the window screen but is partially cut off from the image.
description_1: A close up view of a partially visible tabby cat staring forward with its pale green eyes and closed mouth. The cat's head is facing toward the left with its ears pointed toward the left side of the view. At the bottom of the view a partially visible arm or leg from a human is underneath the cat's head. In the background of the view a cream colored tile square shaped floor can be seen, with light illuminating the floor, as well as the right side of the cats face and side of its body.
